  05 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> spice-gtk-0.7.159.ebuild,
  spice-gtk-0.8.ebuild, spice-gtk-0.11.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

